Detailed Description

Configuration Component Manager API type.

Definition of the command ID

CM_CMD_XXX designates the command ID used by the CM_SetMode routine.

Remarks:
Other command IDs are not yet implemented.

Define Documentation

#define CM_CMD_INTENSIVE_CHECK   ((t_cm_cmd_id)0x100)

Enable/Disable intensive internal check.

Enable/Disable intensive internal check (0=Disable, 1=Enable):

  • Component handle checking

Must be used during the integration phase (additional process is time consuming).

#define CM_CMD_TRACE_LEVEL   ((t_cm_cmd_id)0x80)

Define the level of internal CM log traces.

Define the level of internal CM log traces (-1 to 3)

  1. -1 all internal LOG/ERROR traces are disabled
  2. 0 all internal LOG traces are disabled (default/reset value)
  3. 1, 2, 3 Most and most
